          "reviewBody": "Hi All, my child is studying in Narayana eTechno School, Ramapuram branch, Chennai.. I really feel so proud to be a part of this institution.. All teachers are well educated.. not just that they are so humble towards each child they teach.. as we say  A Good leader can form a good team.. here our Principal Mam and her team of Teachers and every employee form the great team... my child is getting encouraged, motivated and is also being taught the right values of life.. without a blink I can say Trust this school and the management, mainly Ramapuram branch.. it's worth for your child's growth and future endeavours 💐💐💐",
