            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "1. Annual day event went well and kids enjoyed, kids showed lot of maturity. Teachers and trainers put in lot of efforts which was visible. Thank You!\n2. Friendly and caring teachers and teaching is good. My kids are progressing well.\n3. My kind request and may be other parents feels the same., There should be good play ground which helps kids to improve in sports and physical activity. Book fees do not match MRP, since we already pay tuition fees, Annual fees, exam fees and uniform fees but still charging extra for books is not great…., 8000 book fees for 1st standard and 6000 for KG students is way too much…The quality of a school is not only about education. It's about lot more….. Hope the management look into my review and consider our concerns…..",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
